"(define (pict-path-element=? a b)
  (or (eq? a b)
      (if (converted-pict? a)
          (if (converted-pict? b)
              (eq? (converted-pict-parent a) (converted-pict-parent b))
              (eq? (converted-pict-parent a) b))
          (if (converted-pict? b)
              (eq? (converted-pict-parent b) a)
              #f))))
"
